# defs --- define the environment for autogen tests.
#
# Time-stamp:     "2006-01-28 15:46:54 bkorb"
# Author:         Bruce Korb <bkorb@gnu.org>
# Maintainer:     Bruce Korb <bkorb@gnu.org>
